/* ClothesSection Start */
.clothesImageContainer {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.clothesImageContainer:hover img{
  transform: scale(1.07, 1.07);
  transition: all 1.0s;
}


.clothesImageContainer .clothesImageContent{
  position: absolute;
  top: 0px;
  background-color: rgba(240, 255, 255, 0.374);
  color: aliceblue;
  padding: 0px 8px;
  height: 100%;
  width: 100%;
  transform: perspective(400px) rotateY(90deg);
  transform-origin: left;
  /* right: 0; */
  /* transform: perspective(400px) rotateY(-90deg); */
  /* transform-origin: right; */
  box-sizing: border-box;
  transition: all 0.5s;
}

.clothesImageContainer:hover .clothesImageContent{
  transform: perspective(400px) rotateY(0deg);
}
